	Content:
		Documents allow you to insert content. They are **the pages**.
		There is no limitation on what a document can contain, so 
		almost any content can be created:
		
		* Home page
		* Subject topic
		* Book chapter
		* Terms of use
		* ...
		
	Header: Document Structure
	
	Content: 
		A document is a text in [SemanticText](https://semantictext.info),
		that follows the following namespace:
		
